    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>At room temperature, SARS-CoV-2 was stable on environmental surfaces and remained viable up to 7 days on smooth surfaces. This virus could survive for several hours in feces and 3-4 days in urine.</jats:p>",
